88
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:48,410
I'm going to quit all social media to practice!

89
00:05:48,410 --> 00:05:52,500
Chris, like I keep saying, 
just go at your own pace.

90
00:05:52,500 --> 00:05:53,790
Right.

91
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:55,460
Chris!

92
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:56,990
Next, in fifth after the short program,

93
00:05:56,990 --> 00:06:00,250
Christophe Giacometti, 
representing Switzerland, age 25.

94
00:06:01,610 --> 00:06:03,910
He is skating to "Rapsodie Espagnole."

95
00:06:04,580 --> 00:06:06,960
An error in the short program 
caused his technical score

96
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:10,050
to fall below that of China's Guang-hong Ji,

97
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:13,430
