218
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:11,470
But this time, I'm anxious because my 
mistakes would reflect on you, too!

219
00:13:11,470 --> 00:13:15,100
I've been wondering if you secretly want to quit!

220
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:16,750
Of course I don't.

221
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:17,950
I know!

222
00:13:20,570 --> 00:13:22,770
I'm not good with people crying in front of me.

223
00:13:22,770 --> 00:13:25,490
I don't know what I should do.

224
00:13:25,490 --> 00:13:27,260
Should I just kiss you or something?

225
00:13:27,260 --> 00:13:28,240
No!

226
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:31,310
Just have more faith than I do that I'll win!

227
00:13:31,310 --> 00:13:35,120
You don't have to say anything. 
Just stand by me!

